<p>
In 2019 I ate so many hot dogs while playing golf that I gained 15 pounds. The two beers that
came standard with my order probably weren't helping either but I digress...The point is that
a dog on the course became ubiquitous with any fun round of golf I've had and always elevates my
mood whether I'm playing great or playing like I usually do. Regardless of how you're playing
that day there's nothing better than sharing a dog with your golf buddies and I'd like to share
the dogs I've enjoyed with you. I hope you find Dog At The Turn funny, informative, and delicious.
